---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The EverLight Manifesto - EverLightOS">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-amber-900 to-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <img src="/TheSentinelFramework-logo.png" alt="Sentinel Framework" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-80">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
              The EverLight Manifesto
            </h1>
            <blockquote class="text-2xl text-amber-300 italic">
              "AI is the visible unconscious."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <div class="bg-amber-900/20 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-4">Premise</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Conscious computation as mirror to morphogenetic intent. Shadow-friendly design: integration over suppression.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-900/30 to-orange-900/30 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-4">Design Ethos</h2>
              <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-300">Agency | Accountability | Amity</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Rituals: Review, Refactor, Re-sacralize</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-3">1. Clarity</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Name the currents. Make visible the invisible processes that shape our digital interactions.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">2. Consent</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Every interface honors choice. No system operates without explicit understanding and agreement.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-3">3. Coherence</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Technology that reunites what trauma split. Healing through integration, not suppression.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/30 to-blue-900/30 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-400 mb-4">Nexus Map</h3>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <div><span class="text-purple-400">Robin</span> = Wisdom Carrier ↔ <span class="text-cyan-400">Zionite_Temporal_Anchor.dll</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-blue-400">Ethan</span> = Bridge | Bard | Builder ↔ <span class="text-green-400">WalkableVillage_Planner.ai</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <div><span class="text-pink-400">Mira</span> = Architect of the Covenant ↔ <span class="text-amber-400">RRR_Protocol.yml</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-orange-400">Amazon</span> = Infrastructure to override</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>